<lb n="0568c12" ed="T"/>　賀梨　寐帝　乾途　婆賀羅　莎呵</p>
<lb n="0568c13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0568c1301">復次我今燒眾名香。運心供養須耶門<app type="star" corresp="#0568030"><lem wit="【大】">天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">大</rdg></app>王
